But what about all these other
design variables?

154
00:08:05,794 --> 00:08:08,655
They include factors
such as existing infrastructure

155
00:08:08,855 --> 00:08:11,569
and services, 
skills and capacities,

156
00:08:11,769 --> 00:08:14,769
legal requirements, 
regulations,

157
00:08:14,969 --> 00:08:19,242
norms, social acceptance,
operational maintenance,

158
00:08:19,442 --> 00:08:21,155
financial liability.

159
00:08:21,355 --> 00:08:25,217
As engineers and practitioners
working in faecal sludge management

160
00:08:25,430 --> 00:08:29,120
we need to fill many different roles
and realize the importance

161
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:31,136
of why solutions will fail

162
00:08:31,336 --> 00:08:33,951
if not part of this larger approach.

163
00:08:34,151 --> 00:08:37,203
As we will introduce in week 4

164
00:08:37,403 --> 00:08:40,677
this is where a planning framework
helps you to determine relevant

165
00:08:40,877 --> 00:08:42,494
design variables.

166
00:08:42,694 --> 00:08:45,911
And when in a project cycle
to consider them.

167
00:08:46,111 --> 00:08:51,464
A framework will guide practitioners
from the initial project planning phase

168
00:08:51,664 --> 00:08:55,525
to implementation and ongoing 
operations and maintenance.

169
