In week 4 we will introduce
planning and management aspects

170
00:09:01,398 --> 00:09:02,949
of an integrated approach

171
00:09:03,149 --> 00:09:04,864
that helped form the foundation

172
00:09:05,064 --> 00:09:08,167
that longterm successful systems
are built on.

173
